measure.CatchLine: Appropriates moneys from the General Fund to the Housing and Community Services Department for the purpose of making matching deposits into individual development accounts.
measure.MeasureSummary:
Digest: The Act funds matching deposits for IDA accounts. (Flesch Readability Score: 61.2). 
	Appropriates moneys from the General Fund to the Housing and Community Services Department for the purpose of making matching deposits into individual development accounts. 
	Declares an emergency, effective on passage.
measure.RelatingToFull: Relating to individual development accounts; and declaring an emergency.
measure.RelatingTo: Relating to individual development accounts; declaring an emergency.

historyActions.ActionText: First reading. Referred to Speaker's desk.
Referred to Early Childhood and Human Services with subsequent referral to Ways and Means.
Recommendation: Do pass and be referred to Ways and Means by prior reference.
Referred to Ways and Means by prior reference.
